                <p>(a) <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <supplied reason="lost">Untel</supplied> fils de <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>kartès, <supplied reason="lost">Untel</supplied> fils de Lysis,
